I&#039;ve always loved the look and feel of the warden and marauder skins and you&#039;d think that these two skinlines would be a regular thing considering they represent the opposing sides of the games main map: summoners rift 

With pool party, Project, arcade becoming almost yearly skins I&#039;d hope that one day this would apply the same too wardens/marauders because they touch on the heart of Summoners rift: epic battles 

And who wouldn&#039;t want to go into a epic battle with sweet dark or light armour 
Depending on which side of the map the champion fits
1) magelords or marauders
2) Protectorate or wardens

And if riot decides to touch on this skinline again these are the champions I&#039;d hope to see portrayed in each side

